you're doing fine ♪</i>

20:42.825 --> 20:45.745
<i>♪ My love,
the pleasure's mine ♪</i>

20:45.745 --> 20:49.374
<i>♪ Let me go crazy on you ♪</i>

20:49.374 --> 20:53.252
<i>♪ Crazy on you ♪</i>

20:53.252 --> 20:55.463
<i>♪ Crazy on ♪</i>

20:57.090 --> 20:59.175
Everyone enjoying themselves?

21:01.135 --> 21:03.054
Your unit is disbanded.

21:03.054 --> 21:06.933
Each and every one of you
will be disciplined.

21:06.933 --> 21:08.977
Maybe not officially.

21:08.977 --> 21:12.730
But rest assured, Uncle Sam
will get his pound of flesh,

21:12.730 --> 21:14.732
and I--

21:14.732 --> 21:18.403
well, I just got my ass handed
to me by the colonel himself.

21:18.403 --> 21:21.489
And you've decided
to throw a goddamn party!

21:23.491 --> 21:26.077
Don't stand at attention
like you respect me.

21:27.120 --> 21:30.915
I told you how
I wanted this case wrapped up.

21:30.915 --> 21:32.333
Yes, sir.

21:32.333 --> 21:34.544
Why'd you fuck me?

21:34.544 --> 21:38.047
If you're looking for an
apology, there isn't one coming.

21:39.298 --> 21:40.967
You know,

21:40.967 --> 21:43.970
when you first got the 110th,

21:43.970 --> 21:45.596
all the brass said that

21:45.596 --> 21:48.599
you would eventually fuck it up.

21:48.599 --> 21:50.768
Glad I didn't disappoint.

21:52.311 --> 21:54.355
110th...

21:54.355 --> 21:57.400
Special Investigators Unit,

21:57.400 --> 22:00.111
you're all hereby
relieved of your duty.

