- Wish I had my piece.
- Any decent cop

23:01.881 --> 23:04.175
would see the outline
of a weapon in these scrubs.

23:04.175 --> 23:06.594
We go in nice and easy,
get the info we need

23:06.594 --> 23:08.221
and we're gone.

23:08.221 --> 23:09.847
Fine.

23:09.847 --> 23:12.433
But nothing with you
is ever nice and easy.

23:19.690 --> 23:21.234
Hi, Grant.

23:21.234 --> 23:23.402
You yell or make noise,
I'll tear your trachea out

23:23.402 --> 23:25.613
and your last thought'll be,
"Holy shit, he really did it."

23:25.613 --> 23:27.615
When and where
is Langston meeting his buyer?

23:27.615 --> 23:30.409
- I don't know.
- I think you do.

23:30.409 --> 23:32.328
You're a loose end who's
gonna be questioned as soon as

23:32.328 --> 23:34.122
he's medically cleared.
You don't think Langston

23:34.122 --> 23:36.916
has someone on the way here
right now to take you out?

23:36.916 --> 23:38.709
I don't know anything.

23:47.176 --> 23:49.303
Let's make sure.

23:54.559 --> 23:57.478
What the hell?

24:01.941 --> 24:03.359
What are you doing?

24:04.318 --> 24:06.362
Hey! What are...

24:06.362 --> 24:08.281
Shh, shh, shh, shh,
shh, shh, shh, shh.

24:08.281 --> 24:09.699
You know
how a catheter works?

24:09.699 --> 24:11.159
There's a balloon inflated
in your bladder

24:11.159 --> 24:13.077
holding it in place.

24:13.077 --> 24:14.912
If I fill the balloon port
with air, it'll burst

24:14.912 --> 24:18.166
the balloon and tear your
urethra apart like a piñata.

24:18.166 --> 24:20.209
I've messed up a lot of guys
a lot of ways,

24:20.209 --> 24:22.253
but I've never done that.

24:22.253 --> 24:24.797
To be honest, I'm kind of
curious how you'll react.

24:24.797 --> 24:27.091
So if I were you,
I'd start talking.

24:29.969 --> 24:32.305
Okay, here we go.

24:45.193 --> 24:47.486
I can't understand
a word he's saying.

24:52.116 --> 24:53.701
Okay, okay. Fuck.

24:53.701 --> 24:56.162
Fuck.

24:56.162 --> 24:57.413
Langston's meeting
the buyer tomorrow.

24:57.413 --> 24:58.915
- What time?
- Five a.m.

24:58.915 --> 25:00.333
Where?

25:00.333 --> 25:03.252
Langston keeps things
on a need-to-know basis.

25:04.337 --> 25:06.339
That's it, I swear.

25:09.133 --> 25:11.510
Fuck!

25:11.510 --> 25:13.596
Keep it the hell down, buddy.

25:21.020 --> 25:23.022
I swear to God...

25:23.022 --> 25:25.316
I told you all I know.

25:30.780 --> 25:32.406
Lucky for you,
it looks suspicious

25:32.406 --> 25:33.616
when your insides blow up.

25:33.616 --> 25:35.910
Hospital checks
security cameras,

25:35.910 --> 25:39.163
sees us coming in here,
causes all kinds of trouble.

25:41.374 --> 25:43.709
But if you have an embolism
after a car accident...

25:47.546 --> 25:49.715
...no one suspects a thing.

25:49.715 --> 25:51.008
What?

25:52.051 --> 25:55.513
A gift... from Gaitano Russo.

25:57.014 --> 25:58.975
No.

26:13.823 --> 26:15.741
- Hurry! Over here! Come here!
- Out of the way, please.

26:15.741 --> 26:16.951
- He's flatlining.
- Hands on deck.

26:16.951 --> 26:18.202
I need a crash cart!

26:18.202 --> 26:20.288
We have a Code Blue!
Move, move!

26:20.288 --> 26:22.707
That way.

26:30.464 --> 26:32.758
Up ahead.
Doctor scrubs, but look

26:32.758 --> 26:34.927
at the stethoscope.
Only nurses carry paper tape.

26:34.927 --> 26:36.846
Looks like
he grabbed what he could

26:36.846 --> 26:38.556
and threw it on,
just like we did.

26:38.556 --> 26:40.308
Langston hates loose ends.

26:40.308 --> 26:42.476
Doc's coming for Grant.

26:43.519 --> 26:44.603
Oh!

28:38.551 --> 28:40.428
Fuck you!

28:54.733 --> 28:56.735
Shit.

28:56.735 --> 28:58.904
I wanted to question him.

29:09.290 --> 29:12.751
Maybe we can still
get some answers?

29:14.462 --> 29:16.797
Give me some good news.

29:16.797 --> 29:18.883
Sure. You're down another man,

29:18.883 --> 29:21.093
but I left his body
in the morgue for convenience.

29:24.847 --> 29:26.765
Oh, that's okay.

29:26.765 --> 29:29.560
Since you've made it a habit
of taking out my guys,

29:29.560 --> 29:32.229
I've come up
with my own contingency plan

29:32.229 --> 29:33.814
<i>and I've got two of your guys.</i>

29:33.814 --> 29:35.399
Bullshit.

29:35.399 --> 29:38.444
<i>See, I still know people
in the police department.</i>

29:38.444 --> 29:41.238
And after the untimely death
of Officer Russo,

29:41.238 --> 29:44.200
I had the GPS
on his precinct car run.

29:44.200 --> 29:48.078
Nothing unusual, except for
a visit to the Jade East Motel,

29:48.078 --> 29:50.164
a by-the-hour tug joint

29:50.164 --> 29:52.166
that that Boy Scout
would never visit

29:52.166 --> 29:53.626
unless he was working a case.

29:53.626 --> 29:55.628
<i>Just so happened
it was the same night</i>

29:55.628 --> 29:58.506
<i>as a hell of a fender-bender
in the New Age lobby.</i>

29:58.506 --> 30:00.674
So, today,

30:00.674 --> 30:02.676
I sent some of my boys
over there

30:02.676 --> 30:05.095
and guess what they found?

30:05.095 --> 30:06.472
Your pals.

30:06.472 --> 30:07.723
What do you want?

30:07.723 --> 30:09.975
<i>I got an R & D facility
in Rockland County.</i>

30:09.975 --> 30:12.394
<i>You and your buddy
surrender your weapon</i>

30:12.394 --> 30:16.148
<i>and stay under the watch of
my men there till this is over.</i>

30:16.148 --> 30:18.317
<i>And then
I'll let you all go, alive.</i>

30:18.317 --> 30:20.069
Says a guy
who doesn't like loose ends.

30:20.069 --> 30:22.488
<i>You know, this has gone
way too far.</i>

30:22.488 --> 30:25.157
<i>But soon, my associates
and I will have $65 million</i>

30:25.157 --> 30:27.201
and we won't have a reason
to kill you.

30:27.201 --> 30:30.663
More bodies means
more bullshit, so you

30:30.663 --> 30:32.623
<i>and your cohort come here,</i>

30:32.623 --> 30:35.251
<i>and this is over for all of us
before you know it.</i>

30:35.251 --> 30:37.378
My cohort's name is Neagley.

30:37.378 --> 30:39.296
And she's dead.

30:40.339 --> 30:41.924
Your guy killed her
in the hospital basement.

30:41.924 --> 30:44.051
Then I slit his jugular
with a bone saw.

30:44.051 --> 30:46.804
Then you come here now.

30:46.804 --> 30:48.722
But if you fuck around
and call the cops,

30:48.722 --> 30:50.516
I'll kill the only two friends
you have left.

30:50.516 --> 30:52.017
<i>Cops are already here.</i>

30:52.017 --> 30:53.435
I'm at the scene
of a double homicide

30:53.435 --> 30:54.853
waiting to be questioned.

30:54.853 --> 30:56.522
I leave now,
they start tailing me.

30:56.522 --> 30:57.982
You want them
following me to you?

30:57.982 --> 31:00.109
<i>I'll be there sometime tonight.</i>

31:00.109 --> 31:03.070
When I show up,
I need proof of life.

31:03.070 --> 31:04.738
<i>Oh, you'll get it.</i>

31:04.738 --> 31:08.075
But if you try anything cute,
you'll get proof of death.

31:11.537 --> 31:13.539
Langston was a cop for 30 years.

31:13.539 --> 31:15.165
You don't think
he can pull a few strings

31:15.165 --> 31:16.875
and find out
I'm not at the coroner's?

31:16.875 --> 31:20.254
Eventually. Until then,
I bought us some time.

31:20.254 --> 31:22.047
To do what?

31:25.801 --> 31:27.303
Yeah.

31:27.303 --> 31:29.847
<i>There's a Jack Margrave
on the line for you.</i>

31:29.847 --> 31:32.641
<i>He says it's urgent.</i>

31:32.641 --> 31:34.810
Put him through.

31:37.187 --> 31:40.691
<i>- Mr. Reacher.</i>
- I'm about to tear
the apple cart to pieces.

31:40.691 --> 31:43.068
You still prepared
to give me everything I need?

31:43.068 --> 31:44.486
<i>One hundred percent.</i>

31:44.486 --> 31:47.448
Your private security--
former SEALs and Rangers?

31:47.448 --> 31:49.533
<i>Two SEALs, one Ranger.</i>

31:49.533 --> 31:51.243
Good. I need 'em.

31:51.243 --> 31:52.786
<i>Well, if that's what
it's gonna take</i>

31:52.786 --> 31:54.288
<i>to make all this go away, done.</i>

31:54.288 --> 31:57.041
Look, Reacher,

31:57.041 --> 32:00.085
I know that you think I'm some
feckless scumbag politician,

32:00.085 --> 32:02.421
but I was just trying
to do right by our country.

32:02.421 --> 32:06.550
<i>Yes, maybe I...
maybe I wet my beak a little.</i>

32:06.550 --> 32:08.844
But I didn't know that
it would lead to people dying.

32:08.844 --> 32:10.304
You got to believe me on that.

32:10.304 --> 32:12.890
You want absolution,
talk to a priest.

32:12.890 --> 32:16.143
Now, here's exactly
what I need you to do.

32:24.610 --> 32:26.779
Lot of
exterior lighting.

32:27.821 --> 32:29.823
Anyone trying to cross
is gonna get lit up

32:29.823 --> 32:32.117
like a Wrigley Field night game.

32:32.117 --> 32:35.829
Not to mention the camera mounts
all around the perimeter.

32:36.872 --> 32:39.041
Langston said if anything
suspicious goes down,

32:39.041 --> 32:40.959
he'll kill Dixon and O'Donnell.

32:42.002 --> 32:43.837
There's no way to initiate
a plan from the outside

32:43.837 --> 32:46.340
without putting them at risk.

32:46.340 --> 32:48.842
That's why I have to do this
from the inside.

32:48.842 --> 32:50.761
Get a jump on 'em.

32:51.929 --> 32:55.015
You're just gonna walk in there?

32:55.015 --> 32:56.767
You have no idea
what he's gonna do to you.

32:56.767 --> 32:58.936
That's not exactly true.

32:58.936 --> 33:01.146
We saw Franz's autopsy record.

33:03.190 --> 33:06.110
Cuffs, torture?

33:06.110 --> 33:08.320
No, Reacher.

33:10.906 --> 33:14.201
Don't worry. I'm not just
gonna lie down and take it.

