Operation Kite Runner lately.

37:05.265 --> 37:07.267
Strange.

37:07.267 --> 37:09.144
So have I.

37:09.144 --> 37:12.230
We went into that case knowing
it was a losing proposition.

37:13.231 --> 37:14.691
And we all got burned.

37:17.527 --> 37:19.321
